milestones.description: Andy Bichel and Shane Watson's 63-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 45 between Max Walker and Laughlin
Atapattu and Jayasuriya's 234-run partnership is SL's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 171 between Atapattu and Jayasuriya
This is the highest match aggregate (607) involving teams Australia & Sri Lanka in ODIs
Atapattu and Jayasuriya's 234-run partnership is SL's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 226 between Mahela Jayawardene and Atapattu
